@startuml
title Query Flow

actor User
participant "Gradio/MCP" as UI
participant "IndexManager" as IDX
participant "HyDE+Zveno" as LLM
participant "Embeddings Server" as EMB
participant "Hybrid Search" as HS
participant "HNSW C++" as HNSW
participant "BM25" as BM25
database "SQLite+Index" as DB

User -> UI: query + corpus path
UI -> IDX: sync on startup
IDX -> DB: diff files, update chunks
IDX -> EMB: embed new chunks
IDX -> HNSW: add/remove vectors
IDX -> BM25: rebuild lexical index

UI -> LLM: HyDE expand query
LLM --> UI: scientific query text
UI -> EMB: embed query
EMB --> UI: query vector
UI -> HS: hybrid search
HS -> HNSW: vector top-k
HS -> BM25: lexical top-k
HS --> UI: merged chunks
UI -> LLM: answer with context
LLM --> User: answer or not-found message
@enduml
